  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\n*Summary*: There was a report on Instabug about not being able to complete a transaction in DDEX dapp. There was `The method eth_sign does not exists/is not available` error on 0.9.25, Android 25:\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/44787546-c054e280-ab97-11e8-87df-19d4d6ea1ea6.png\" width=\"200\">\r\n\r\nThis is expected behavior as Status does not support the deprecated web3 method `eth_sign`. In the case of DApps using deprecated methods, it would be useful to communicate to the user that blockers are a form of security protection.\r\n\r\n[Slack conversation](https://status-im.slack.com/archives/C9P233D54/p1535460012000100) about the issue.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open DDEX from dapp list\r\n- Try to buy some token\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: 0.9.26\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\nLogs: from 00:01 - https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803590-status/builds/8574965/sessions/4399986360/?accessToken=kgi3ucCssbpn6rQWVgyScBQvRuU\r\n```\r\n...\r\n...\r\n07:55 D/WebViewBridgeManager: headers {Source=ddex-web, Jwt-Authentication=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJhY2NvdW50IjoiMHg2ZjJmOWYxOTUxMmM5MTlmMWIyNjVlYmZlOWIyYWRmNDRlNzVkMGNkIiwic2Vzc2lvbklkIjoiNmUxZGIxNTktODNiMC00YzZiLTg1NjgtODU1ZDkwNmJjNzc1IiwiaWF0IjoxNTM1NzA0MTk2LCJleHAiOjE1MzgyOTYxOTYsImlzcyI6IkRERVgifQ.s4lXG325qkHfrKlwQybjWrSLSpclAweZYh8vW3zdyeE, Referer=https://ddex.io/trade/GTO-WETH, Origin=https://ddex.io, Content-Type=application/json;charset=UTF-8, User-Agent=Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 7.0; SM-J730FM Build/NRD90M; wv) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0 Chrome/68.0.3440.91 Mobile Safari/537.36, Accept=application/json, text/plain, */*}\r\n07:55 D/WebViewBridgeManager: method POST\r\n07:55 D/WebViewBridgeManager: shouldInterceptRequest / WebViewClient -> intercept response is nil, delegating up\r\n07:55 D/ReactNativeJS: DEBUG [status-im.utils.transactions:60] - HTTP GET https://api.etherscan.io/api?module=account&action=txlist&address=0x6f2f9f19512c919f1b265ebfe9b2adf44e75d0cd&startblock=0&endblock=99999999&sort=desc&apikey=DMSI4UAAKUBVGCDMVP3H2STAMSAUV7BYFI?q=json\r\n07:55 D/InputMethodManager: HSI from window - flag : 0 Pid : 31427\r\n07:55 D/ReactNativeJS: DEBUG [status-im.utils.handlers:37] - Handling re-frame event:  :update-transactions-success\r\n07:55 D/ReactNativeJS: DEBUG [status-im.utils.handlers:37] - Handling re-frame event:  :on-bridge-message {\"type\":\"web3-send-async\",\"messageId\":204,\"payload\":{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":459,\"method\":\"eth_sign\",\"params\":[\"0x6f2f9f19512c919f1b265ebfe9b2adf44e75d0cd\",\"0xd5c4902d228504769a1241edfc6fd1db5329b40eb87956be19b3ad321573bbc8\"]}}\r\n07:55 D/ReactNativeJS: DEBUG [status-im.utils.handlers:37] - Handling re-frame event:  :send-to-bridge\r\n07:55 I/chromium: [INFO:CONSOLE(1)] \"Uncaught (in promise) Error: The method eth_sign does not exist/is not available\", source: https://cdn.ddex.io/static/js/bundle.4f1693f5.js (1)\r\n07:55 D/StatusNativeLogs: [INFO:CONSOLE(1)] \"Uncaught (in promise) Error: The method eth_sign does not exist/is not available\", source: https://cdn.ddex.\r\n07:55 D/StatusNativeLogs: io/static/js/bundle.4f1693f5.js (1)\r\n07:56 D/ViewRootImpl@c5dd2d7[MainActivity]: ThreadedRenderer.create() translucent=true\r\n07:56 D/InputTransport: Input channel constructed: fd=245\r\n07:56 D/ViewRootImpl@c5dd2d7[MainActivity]: setView = DecorView@37a77c4[MainActivity] touchMode=true\r\n07:56 D/ViewRootImpl@c5dd2d7[MainActivity]: dispatchAttachedToWindow\r\n07:56 D/ViewRootImpl@c5dd2d7[MainActivity]: Relayout returned: oldFrame=[0,0][0,0] newFrame=[28,743][1052,1240] result=0x27 surface={isValid=true 1433061376} surfaceGenerationChanged=true\r\n...\r\n...\r\n...\r\n```\r\n",
