    "body": "I was able to reproduce it on iOS 11.4.1 , Android 7.0 with the latest Develop nightly build (`0.9.26 (7253) node 19b53030`) with Ddex when trading (WETH - GTO / WETH - SNT). In my case it was:\r\n\r\n1) Open Ddex.io\r\n2) Connect your wallet address and wrap WETH for trading\r\n3) Select pair you want to trade  (WETH - GTO in my case)\r\n4) Tap 'Buy GTO' (or your token).\r\n\r\n**Actual result:**  Dapp `Complete your token` modal window appears. Pop-up in Status app `Catch error: The method eth_sign does not exist/is not available` appear. No transactions. ",
